Question: Is the remote made of the same material as the calculator?

Reference Answer: Yes, both the remote and the calculator are made of plastic.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n90294.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='remote')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='calculator')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What material is the remote made of?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What material is the calculator made of?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
